title: Unable to Patch Version Name: 7.18
body:
Hi ,
I tried every to install this Patch but i am not able update it ( **Patch: LOL_patch_20170915to20170919.exe**). It Showing Error " _Failed to Patch: Please Install latest version error:_ "  and this error in install log: 
**Failed to move Game\ZipContents.zip
Failed to merge Game\ZipContents.zip
Failed to apply patch
**

I uninstalled it and re-install the whole game but after installing the game again it ask for update league of legends. When i click for update, same error comes, i downloaded Cafe version, Full client version, i tried for Manual Patch, Hot Fix Patch, disabling the Firewall still same error .

In Garena its showing "_ Your Garena+ and Games are all updated to latest version_". but when click on league of legends it ask for update.
Every time for small updates i have to uninstall whole game and re-download it. 
Please Please Help me out why i am getting this error...??


Regard 
VakY

replies.body: Since I'm on the support for the NA region, I'm not gonna be able to help very much for that Garena installer =\ . Make sure you're running it as admin first, but if that's not helping reach out to the Garena support over here -> http://intl.garena.com/support/
